data.description: Come take a look at this cute, very well maintained house ready for you to call home located in the deed restricted community of Marion Oaks. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home offers just over 1300 sq. ft. Inside you'll find a welcoming floor plan. The living room, dining, and kitchen all flow together while the kitchen also offers a nice eat-in space. With a split for plan you'll have a nice master suite and two spacious guest bedrooms and a guest bath on the other. Outside you'll find peace while enjoying the greenery in the screened porch. This home has been very loved over the years and you'll be sure to do the same. Roof 2015. AC 2016. Located close to restaurants, medical facilities, and shopping, along with easy access to major roads for travel. Come take a look today.
